        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: externalize GMI provider plugin",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Externalizes `@openclaw/gmi-provider` as an official publishable provider plugin with ClawHub/npm install metadata, README, and package-local shrinkwrap.\n- Moves GMI from bundled-provider docs into the official external provider catalog and generated plugin reference/inventory output.\n- Adds coverage for the GMI external catalog/release metadata, and records the QA Lab manifest description so regenerated inventory docs keep its real plugin description while reflecting its contract surface.\n\n## Verification\n\n```bash\npnpm plugins:inventory:check\n```\n\n```text\n$ node scripts/generate-plugin-inventory-doc.mjs --check\n```\n\n```bash\npnpm release:plugins:npm:check -- --plugins @openclaw/gmi-provider\n```\n\n```text\nplugin-npm-release-check: publishable plugin metadata looks OK.\n  - @openclaw/gmi-provider@2026.6.8 (stable, gmi)\n```\n\n```bash\npnpm release:plugins:clawhub:check -- --plugins @openclaw/gmi-provider\n```\n\n```text\nplugin-clawhub-release-check: publishable plugin metadata looks OK.\n  - @openclaw/gmi-provider@2026.6.8 (stable, gmi)\n```\n\n```bash\nclawhub package validate extensions/gmi\n```\n\n```text\nPlugin Inspector: PASS\nBreakages: 0\nWarnings: 0\nFindings: none\n```\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/generate-npm-shrinkwrap.mjs --package-dir extensions/gmi --check\n```\n\n```text\nextensions/gmi: npm-shrinkwrap.json is current.\n```\n\n```bash\nOPENCLAW_VITEST_INCLUDE_FILE=<json-pattern-file> node --no-maglev ./node_modules/vitest/vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.tooling.config.ts\n```\n\n```text\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  12 passed (12)\n```\n\n```bash\nnode --no-maglev ./node_modules/vitest/vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.extensions.config.ts gmi/index.test.ts\n```\n\n```text\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  1 passed (1)\n```\n\n```bash\nnode --no-maglev ./node_modules/vitest/vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.plugins.config.ts\n```\n\n```text\nTest Files  170 passed (170)\nTests  2424 passed (2424)\n```\n\n```bash\nnode --no-maglev ./node_modules/vitest/vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.tooling.config.ts test/plugin-clawhub-release.test.ts test/plugin-npm-release.test.ts\n```\n\n```text\nTest Files  2 passed (2)\nTests  55 passed (55)\n```\n\n```bash\ngit diff --check\n```\n\n## Review Notes\n\n- `openclaw plugins init` changes are intentionally not included here; they will be opened in a separate PR.\n- The normal `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs ...` targeted run was blocked by another local worktree's heavy-check lock, so the equivalent scoped Vitest configs above were run directly.\n",
